# Input

```scss
[href]:hover &,// hover
[href]:focus &,// focus
[href]:active &{.tooltip{opacity:1;}}

.powerPathNavigator .helm button.pressedButton,// pressed
.powerPathNavigator .helm button:active:not(.disabledButton){}

```


# Formatted

```scss
[href]:hover &, // hover
[href]:focus &, // focus
[href]:active & {
	.tooltip {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

.powerPathNavigator .helm button.pressedButton, // pressed
.powerPathNavigator .helm button:active:not(.disabledButton) {
}

```
